00:05:10.070 --> 00:05:11.040
what you do.

00:05:11.040 --> 00:05:13.670
We all have to get up
on stage at some point.

00:05:13.670 --> 00:05:15.750
In fact, I have become
convinced that there

00:05:15.750 --> 00:05:19.200
is nothing that is more
important for our professional

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:23.070
success-- and in many cases, our
personal success-- than being

00:05:23.070 --> 00:05:26.240
able to get up in front of other
people and share our ideas.

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:30.510
But here are-- OK, Google
